author: rhillegas
msg: It looks as though a cut-and-paste error duplicated the contents of conrefs.dita. This, in turn created an unparseable dita file and broke the build of adminguide. I have pruned out the duplicate contents. Now adminguide builds cleanly.

author: ayza
msg: Applying patch from HARMONY-3479 ([classlib][swing][netbeans] TransferHandler.getPasteAction().actionPerformed() doesn't check if accessClipboard is allowed). TransferHandlerTest was removed from the exclude list for IBM VME.
